{"tid":819081,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"如果有人有兩隻唔同size嘅左腳 我送呢對鞋比佢","createTime":"2018-09-14T14:00:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-14T15:24:34.000Z","uid":171561,"like":56,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"2cdc3352e8f0e26d6a2a62590df8658c6f96c482","tid":819081,"uid":171561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T14:00:34.000Z","msg":"幾個月前趁間鋪執粒清貨買左對鞋<br />\n試好左買完就放係屋企擺<br />\n等着舊左其他鞋先開新鞋<br />\n<br />\n等到今日終於打開個鞋盒<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/14/214105_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F14%2F214105_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=b7cf9970&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n望落去好正常<br />\n着完落左腳都仲未覺得有咩問題<br />\n<br />\n點知一攞起另一隻先發現...<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/14/214405_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F14%2F214405_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=37e2b226&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">兩隻都係左腳!</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/14/214533_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F14%2F214533_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=5528a6ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一隻42 一隻43碼<br />\n<br />\n仲要間鋪已經執左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n呢個時候 我仲急中生智咁同呀媽講<br />\n買多一對鞋咪可以湊夠兩對lor!<br />\n原來意外發生既時候 人嘅智商係會下降<br />\n<br />\n如果肥絲問我有冇買埋右<br />\n唔係我唔想買 係想買都買唔到<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n對鞋六百幾 唔想晒左佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果有會員有兩隻左腳就留tg啦"},{"pid":"fff2c84fdf7cc25ca72fb206565db011f65dfd62","tid":819081,"uid":149357,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T14:03:48.000Z","msg":"可能你就係多左隻左腳<br />\n少左個腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2710349517687d9be6db2cfc54b5cfca2c29a38","tid":819081,"uid":182334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T14:08:21.000Z","msg":"佢痴q左線呀"},{"pid":"3c043f0d072eccdc415f58cbfe6a7e23d462f8ed","tid":819081,"uid":129712,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T14:10:12.000Z","msg":"真心咩"},{"pid":"cf4322b77c9e2238b98466318ded711bbd2fe187","tid":819081,"uid":28800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T14:11:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4634cf2c7f1bef01623cdeea7a4efaea43bf2c4f","tid":819081,"uid":46943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T14:13:39.000Z","msg":"我地加埋有四隻左腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n無右<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0bf3401b5e2768a378a657f87c666a84f64b8da","tid":819081,"uid":90499,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T14:15:43.000Z","msg":"唔錯，8/10"},{"pid":"728e7f3be35884c9048d0968ce2dc375dc77f871","tid":819081,"uid":8167,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T14:17:28.000Z","msg":"咁核突 點會買得落手"},{"pid":"4b8da3b0aa536c7f2eaba7515a7775910a0eb613","tid":819081,"uid":194882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T14:17:39.000Z","msg":"排球鞋？"},{"pid":"d7b5f81278e16cafc877e2985f003b1b89e7266a","tid":819081,"uid":103325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T14:18:29.000Z","msg":"中間個隻腳著唔著到？"},{"pid":"e5a7bd9e50a8117ca3b471eb9d40ac6ddbadc76d","tid":819081,"uid":152003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T14:20:45.000Z","msg":"咁應該有人係兩隻右腳 你搵得返佢就可以合返一對<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f1c936413bf2e228db203717f479cb630012c59","tid":819081,"uid":171561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T14:54:55.000Z","msg":"其實而家唔上唔落<br />\ndup左佢又覺得浪費<br />\n擺係度又晒位<br />\n<br />\n有冇得直接同代理商講叫佢幫幫手<br />\n歸究都位店員嘅錯 但係佢執左粒已經冇可能搵番佢負責任<br />\n<br />\n可能有人買左兩隻右嘅 如果有嘅記住同我相認番<br />\n又可能仲係佢個倉度<br />\n有冇人知間鋪如果賣唔晒執粒個時會點處理?"},{"pid":"94a5f273d0616932ecb507df643a85cd960e9823","tid":819081,"uid":171561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4b8da3b0aa536c7f2eaba7515a7775910a0eb613","tid":819081,"uid":194882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T14:17:39.000Z","msg":"排球鞋？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T14:56:32.000Z","msg":"行山鞋"},{"pid":"dadd534a757eac0b774162f03fed714f230bee75","tid":819081,"uid":3122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T14:57:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7aa184a0742a5af67b29e712029dacc6fda2494","tid":819081,"uid":171561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T15:02:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實而家唔上唔落<br />\ndup左佢又覺得浪費<br />\n擺係度又晒位<br />\n<br />\n有冇得直接同代理商講叫佢幫幫手<br />\n歸<span style=\"color: red;\">咎</span>都<span style=\"color: red;\">係</span>店員嘅錯 但係佢執左粒已經冇可能搵番佢負責任<br />\n<br />\n可能有人買左兩隻右嘅 如果有嘅記住同我相認番<br />\n又可能仲係佢個倉度<br />\n有冇人知間鋪如果賣唔晒執粒個時會點處理d貨?</blockquote>"},{"pid":"e12465b605236af369fac4408f733f256cc4f706","tid":819081,"uid":833,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T15:07:10.000Z","msg":"買多一對正常既<br />\n<br />\n集中訓練左腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d94451fb0467b6375e252b24adb658cd1d504164","tid":819081,"uid":189638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T15:24:34.000Z","msg":"睇下有冇另外買咗兩隻右腳嘅同佢交換。"}]}